ot effect that returns the card isn’t an ability that goes on the stack, it won’t cease to exist along with the leaving player’s spells and abilities on the stack.','W',NULL,'0.05','0.22','0.54',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'放逐する僧侶',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'クリーチャー ― 人間・クレリック',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'放逐する僧侶が戦場に出たとき、対戦相手がコントロールするクリーチャー１体を対象とし、放逐する僧侶が戦場を離れるまでそれを追放する。（そのクリーチャーはオーナーのコントロール下で戦場に戻る。）',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_「誓い破りめ、失せろ！」_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('394354','Captain of the Watch','EVK','Creature — Human Soldier','R','{4}{W}{W}','6','3','3',NULL,'Vigilance #_(Attacking doesn''t cause this creature to tap.)_#£Other Soldier creatures you control get +1/+1 and have vigilance.£When Captain of the Watch enters the battlefield, create three 1/1 white Soldier creature tokens.',NULL,NULL,'Greg Staples','3','5','£10/1/2009: Captain of the Watch grants +1/+1 and vigilance to all other Soldier creatures you control, not just the ones its ability puts onto the battlefield.','W',NULL,'0.3','0.69','1.49',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'警備隊長',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'クリーチャー ― 人間・兵士',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'警戒£あなたがコントロールする他の兵士・クリーチャーは、＋１/＋１の修整を受けるとともに警戒を持つ。£警備隊長が戦場に出たとき、白の１/１の兵士・クリーチャー・トークンを３体戦場に出す。',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('394355','Celestial Flare','EVK','Instant','C','{W}{W}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target player sacrifices an attacking or blocking creature.','#_"You were defeated the moment you declared your aggression."£—Gideon Jura_#',NULL,'Clint Cearley','4','5','£7/1/2013: Celestial Flare targets only a player, not any creature. A creature with hexproof or protection from white can be sacrificed this way.£7/1/2013: If the player sacrifices a blocking creature,